description:
The Goddess is one of US’s best technical wrestlers; she is fast, strong, elite, and aggressive. The Nightmare
destroyed
her. If you recall, Syd beat the Pirate last season and I thought it was a fluke; however, after she kicked Isis’s ass it’s now official. The Nightmare is the new terror of US. On top of her amazing wrestling, I have never seen a more fierce fucking than The Nightmare gave to the Goddess. She fucked her like a demon from hell, and there was nothing the Goddess could to stop it!
title: The Nightmare vs. The Goddess
